      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FANTASIA QUEEN (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 23.42 beating OPEN ROAD. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Expected to go well again. CRIMSON DYNAMO (3) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.96 beating CHEEKY SLOY. Has good speed and a low draw is a big help. One of the prime contenders. CANYA SUPERSONIC (4) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing third (19.41) in a NG at Bulli. Has a good record here at this journey. Speedy beginner who can find the front with a clean break from the middle of the draw. Expected to be in the finish again. OPEN ROAD (2) among the chances again based on last run here.",
